          <div id="getting">Getting around in Sacramento</div>
          <div></div>
          <p>Sacramento is served by its Sacramento International Airport located 12 miles northwest of downtown Sacramento. This airport is served by all the major domestic full service and low cost carriers that make getting to Sacramento a breeze.<br />
            <br />
            Sacramento is a compact city laid out in a grid like pattern, though like many other cities in California, it offers limited public transport options in the form of the bus and light rail systems. <br />
            <br />
